==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Torpedo-boat destroyer
<hw>Tor*pe"do-boat` de*stroy"er</hw>. <def>A larger, swifter, and more
powerful armed type of torpedo boat, originally intended principally for
the destruction of torpedo boats, but later used also as a more
formidable torpedo boat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Torpedo body</ent>⟦br⟧
